      "value": "<p>To follow this Stylized Looks overview for RenderMan for Katana, make sure to use the great demo scene created by Ernst Janssen Groesbeek of <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.9to3animation.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">9 to 3 Animation</a>:</p><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://pixar-community-large-file-storage.s3-us-west-1.amazonaws.com/RenderMan_24_Beta/RfK/Shipshape_Katana.zip\" rel=\"nofollow\">Download</a></p><p /><iframe align=\"middle\" allowfullscreen=\"\" class=\"conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"false\" data-layout=\"default\" data-local-id=\"3152380a-c6c9-4985-8597-41edd7a621fb\" data-macro-id=\"2d3348026e5ebccbe2cf3bacd3863aa5f85d22298d2660c91ceb65b3093c11e5\" data-macro-name=\"iframe\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"600\" marginwidth=\"960\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-modals allow-orientation-lock allow-pointer-lock allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-presentation allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" scrolling=\"yes\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/524348460\" width=\"960\">\n    \n</iframe>\n<p><br/></p><p>Ship concept by Ian McQue.</p><p>Robot concept by Ruslan Safarov.</p><p>Models by Cheyenne Chapel, Aliya Chen, Damian Kwiatkowski, Alyssa Minko, Anthony Muscarella, and Miguel Zozaya</p><p>© Disney/Pixar - RenderMan &quot;Shipshape&quot; Art Challenge</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em> </em><br/></p>"
